{"tid":510054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[估國家] 4歲男童遭母親等人施暴致死 聖誕節悲劇附近居民震驚","createTime":"2017-12-26T05:22:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T03:19:00.000Z","uid":160094,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7f6cfd559017704bf590678c4c50c70373202d5f","tid":510054,"uid":160094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T05:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://public.potaufeu.asahi.com/0a3d-p/picture/11478159/5b2d910acddbec85459c907dfd189bd5_640px.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpublic.potaufeu.asahi.com%2F0a3d-p%2Fpicture%2F11478159%2F5b2d910acddbec85459c907dfd189bd5_640px.jpg&h=b6f757c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大阪府警方25日對外表示，因在大阪府箕面市集合住宅內的1間房內，對4歲男童施暴並殺害，已依涉嫌殺人逮捕男童的26歲無業母親‧筒井麻衣嫌犯、筒井的24歲無業交往對象‧松本匠吾嫌犯、以及20歲的無業熟人‧大倉敏彌嫌犯，3人均為住戶。<br />\n<br />\n　　男童全身有數十處瘀青，3人供稱:「平時就會(對男童)施暴。」府警研判，男童曾反覆遭到嚴重虐待。<br />\n<br />\n　　根據搜查1課表示，死者為筒井嫌犯的長男步夢。24日深夜至25日凌晨期間，3人施暴毆打步夢的腹部等，涉嫌殺害。步夢的眼周與腹部皆有瘀青，疑似遭到強烈毆打，死因是外傷性腹內出血。<br />\n<br />\n　　事發現場位在UR都市機構的集合住宅8樓，此處位在大阪單軌電車豐川站西北方約2公里的住宅區。住在集合住宅區附近、經營公司的57歲男性，當天凌晨2點過後曾因警笛聲醒來。從陽台望去後，發現集合住宅區有巡邏車閃著警示燈。由於在附近沒聽過孩子的尖叫聲，因此男性震驚地表示:「竟有這麼小的孩子在聖誕夜死亡。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://dessertryouri.site/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/tutui-300x168.bmp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdessertryouri.site%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2Ftutui-300x168.bmp&h=10040ed7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd3c8e557c35cf6db714dbdb95907e63e7d113dd","tid":510054,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T05:24:06.000Z","msg":"Gantz<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c2f83a808174c47a2e65502f0e10b4e653d9b0","tid":510054,"uid":86097,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T05:24:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a510c3418f72ac324aea73b8f2f8aa5bebcca4a4","tid":510054,"uid":10726,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T05:25:50.000Z","msg":"樓上有眼疾"},{"pid":"f93b1ef92af657bcf080b0c25ff82d9161f8c3db","tid":510054,"uid":27866,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T05:26:16.000Z","msg":"樓主五毛"},{"pid":"9984f9ac1128e928b75d87c3b80b784edf38c0f0","tid":510054,"uid":24160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"85c2f83a808174c47a2e65502f0e10b4e653d9b0","tid":510054,"uid":86097,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T05:24:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T05:26:38.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - KeithKeith )"},{"pid":"45f159bc24057bf8feea22901315e0351c69b1d2","tid":510054,"uid":160094,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"85c2f83a808174c47a2e65502f0e10b4e653d9b0","tid":510054,"uid":86097,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T05:24:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T05:39:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.furanotogo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/%E7%AD%92%E4%BA%95%E9%BA%BB%E8%A1%A32.bmp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.furanotogo.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F%25E7%25AD%2592%25E4%25BA%2595%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E8%25A1%25A32.bmp&h=b62d57da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\non9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f25aec976f582f3d8c1c9fef1c2eb10199a2f16a","tid":510054,"uid":27866,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T06:32:47.000Z","msg":"啲盲反大陸憤青入到嚟應該又嬲又失望"},{"pid":"564f2075ed46d3d83409c2ee68abab4270f402fc","tid":510054,"uid":148673,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T07:21:05.000Z","msg":"日本醜聞就係五毛最好嘅聖誕禮物"},{"pid":"e837c39aa72b24bcffc7cecd9a7b887f7b1ed219","tid":510054,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T07:22:47.000Z","msg":"cls又係中國"},{"pid":"3b0a00d91e224cb26bea0fd55d4c18